<p align="left" class="style3" style="margin-top: 0;"><span class="style2"><img src="images/heads/cibm_whoweare.gif" width="608" height="26"></span></p>
<table width="933" border="1">
  <tr valign="top">
    <th width="923" scope="col"><span class="style28">ANNUAL SHAREHOLDER MEETING </span></th>
  </tr>
  <tr valign="top">
    <td><p class="style19" style="margin-bottom: 0">&nbsp;</p>
      <p class="style19" style="margin-top: 0;">CIB Marine Bancshares, Inc. has scheduled its annual meeting of shareholders to be held at 1:30 p.m., local time, on Thursday, May 29, 2008, at the Doubletree Hotel, 5000 West 127th Street, Alsip, Illinois.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
      <p class="style19"><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;"><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;">All shareholders of record <span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;"><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;">of our outstanding shares of common stock </span></span></span></span>at the close of business on March 20, 2008,   will be entitled to vote at the Annual Meeting.</span></span></span></span></p>
      <p class="style19"><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;"><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;"><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:15px;">The Proxy Statement and 2007 Annual Report on Form 10-K are available at <a href="financial_info/sec_filings.asp">http://www.cibmarine.com/financial_info/sec_filings.asp</a>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="style30">The meeting will begin promptly at 1:30 p.m. The order of the meeting is (1) an introduction by Stanley J. Calderon, Chairman of the Board, (2) the election of directors, (3) a presentation by Edwin J. Depenbrok, Chief Financial Officer, (4) remarks by John P. Hickey, President and CEO, and (5) a question and comment period.</p>
</td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<table width="932" border="1">
  <tr valign="top">
    <th width="922" height="30" scope="col"><span class="style18"><span class="style12">TELECONFERENCE&nbsp; INSTRUCTIONS </span></span></th>
  </tr>
  <tr valign="top">
    <td height="120"><p class="style19"><span class="style9" style="font-family:Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif;font-size:13px;">If you are unable to attend the annual meeting in person, you may listen to the meeting by teleconference.&nbsp; In order to access the teleconference of the meeting, please dial 1-800-894-5910 (domestic).&nbsp; Please provide conference ID &ldquo;CIB Marine&rdquo; and program title &ldquo;CIB Marine&rdquo; to the greeter in order to access the conference call.&nbsp; Please note that listening to the teleconference at the meeting will not constitute attendance at the meeting for purposes of determining a quorum.&nbsp; In addition, you will not be able to vote via teleconference.&nbsp; Accordingly, even if you intend to participate in the teleconference, it is important for you to return your completed proxy card to us in advance of the meeting in order for your attendance and vote to be counted.</span></p>
      <p class="style19" style="margin-bottom: 0;">A copy of Mr. Depenbrok's presentation is available <a href="documents/PresentationFinal.pdf">here</a>. </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
